Speaker 1: Hi, my name is Gary Hornaday, I need to cancel my prescription to make sure I'm not billed.

Speaker 2: Anymore.

Speaker 1: Okay, Riverview, Florida?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: Gotcha, it looks like you're a VIP member here, Gary, are you just overstocked right now?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: Okay, completely understandable, especially if you're overstocked right now.

Speaker 2: With your VIP status, Gary, you do get some perks that you're able to utilize.

Speaker 1: If you'd like, we can pause, freeze your account, whatever you want to call it, for the next six months, that way you've got some time to use up what you've got.

Speaker 2: After that, it wouldn't come how it has been every two months, it'd be like whenever you need it after that.

Speaker 1: I'd rather just cancel now.

Speaker 2: If I want to start again, I'll give it a hold, I'll give it a start again.

Speaker 1: Okay, are you sure you don't want to just pause everything?

Speaker 2: It's always better that way, so that the prescription's always just in your back pocket and just work with us on when it's needed and when it's not needed.

Speaker 1: You're going to have to call it regardless.

Speaker 2: The problem with that is I'd have to remember six months from now and all that.

Speaker 1: Are you able to write it down?

Speaker 2: I have everybody write it down on the pill bottle or write it down on their calendar.

Speaker 1: What is the date?

Speaker 2: It would be July 27th.

Speaker 1: If you freeze it, I'll make myself a note and contact you again if I don't need it cancelled.

Speaker 2: I haven't been shipped or billed recently, right?

Speaker 1: Nothing.

Speaker 2: Negative.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: That sounds good to me.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Sounds good, Gary.

Speaker 1: If you ever need me again, my extension is 0040.

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: Thanks so much.

Speaker 2: Absolutely.

Speaker 1: Have a great one.

Speaker 2: Bye.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.

Speaker 2: Bye.

Speaker 1: Bye.

Speaker 2: Bye.
